No 'Sadako' is registered in either
Dr lkuma's or her mother's records.

18
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:45,151
What's happened to Dr lkuma?

19
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,918
He died, soon after
the place was sold.

20
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:54,797
So I'm the only one left alive.

21
